  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are studying the impact of RPh201 on chronic vegetative patients. RPh201
      has been reported to induce neuronal regeneration in animal models. Evaluation will be done
      by combining clinical /behavioral assessment with fMRI studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
